==English==

===Verb===
'''[[blow]] [[chunks]]'''
#{{idiom}} {{colloquial}} To be very [[bad]], [[inadequate]], [[unpleasant]], or [[miserable]]; to [[suck]].
#:''The old version was okay, but the new version '''blows chunks'''.''

===Usage notes===
This term may be considered mildly vulgar, or too strong for use in polite company.